## How this repository works

This repo uses the **em-development-framework**, a 6-step ticket lifecycle backed by a LangGraph engine. Code changes follow `enrich-us → plan → develop → verify → commit → update-docs`. Copilot suggestions land inside the **develop** phase of a ticket whose plan has already been drafted and reviewed.

If you are asked to implement something without a ticket and plan in place, surface this to the operator and ask them to start the lifecycle first:

```bash
python3 -m framework.cli.run --mode lifecycle --ticket <TICKET-ID> --module <module> --work-impl claude --advance
```

